M_n
   \mathsf E[M_{n+1}|X_1,\dots,X_n] = M_n\cdot\mathsf E[X_{n+1}^{e_{n+1}}] 
   \mathsf E[X_{n+1}^{e_{n+1}}] = p\cdot\mathsf E X_{n+1}+(1-p)\cdot\mathsf E X_{n+1}^2 = p(m-\sigma^2)+\sigma^2 
   p = \frac{1-\sigma^2}{m-\sigma^2}. 
